{"tid":1391459,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對抗藍絲廢老必勝秘訣","createTime":"2019-07-31T12:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T14:54:30.000Z","uid":146505,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ad9fc90705ed44ce0ec1dbfa10c77c80a6050bb7","tid":1391459,"uid":146505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:25:35.000Z","msg":"同藍絲廢老理論 <br />\n講道理 講理據 講邏輯 = 對牛彈琴<br />\n<br />\n只有曲線+假膠先可以間接感化佢哋<br />\n<br />\n家有兩老都係 典型深藍愛國阿婆阿伯<br />\n相信大家都試過據理力爭每次都唔愉快收場<br />\n始終係老豆老母 無謂搞到家庭不和睦<br />\n<br />\n跟住我買咗兩件我愛中國嘅tshirt著<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKP8b6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKP8b6h.jpg&h=d9dc80c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同佢哋講我仲愛國過佢哋<br />\n然後講咩都會變啱<br />\n例如可以話愛中國愛香港 先應該聲討黑警 保衛我哋中國香港國際形象<br />\n俾著喺中國 我國嘅公安一定唔會勾結黑幫欺負市民<br />\n佢哋絕對唔會為咗捍衛啲黑警或者香港政府而放棄自己愛中國嘅情懷去同你爭執<br />\n最後就要逼不得已認同你<br />\n<br />\n仲可以叫佢哋唱全首國歌俾你聽證明佢哋愛國<br />\n多數佢哋都會唱錯幾句歌詞<br />\n跟住又可以指責佢觸犯國歌法<br />\n<br />\n只要企喺愛國嘅高地同佢哋辯論就冇可能會輸<br />\n而家我屋企兩老都已經慢慢被感化<br />\n開始識得譴責香港黑警勾結黑社會之類<br />\n<br />\n大家仲有咩其他方法可以分享下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da8e0a47c0e91694a33dc14b68393f923b55291","tid":1391459,"uid":263144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:57:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"95a0b6602449b064010e7bb15811e1eee954f5c1","tid":1391459,"uid":198838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:05:09.000Z","msg":"Good idea! 幫你推！"},{"pid":"29363849c07563ca8f517b2d0e468adaeb8d401e","tid":1391459,"uid":61991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:10:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c0dbcfd95d96c901e6a9f871c85f631a274f0e","tid":1391459,"uid":31655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:54:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}